org.gephi.io.importer.plugin.file

Class ImporterVNA

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gephi.io.importer.plugin.file.ImporterVNA
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FileImporter, Importer, LongTask

    public class ImporterVNA
extends Object
implements FileImporter, LongTask
    Netdraw .vna files importer implemented as a simple state machine due to very loose specification of .vna format (http://netwiki.amath.unc.edu/DataFormats/NetDrawVna).
    Author:
    Vojtech Bardiovsky
